<h2>Chapter 8: Measuring What Actually Matters &#123;#ch8&#125;</h2>
<p>Vanity metrics kill amplification strategies. A post with 10,000 views and zero conversions is not a success. It is a waste of attention.</p>
<p>The key is to measure amplification by funnel stage. Different metrics matter at different stages.</p>
